1 shall carry forward. Projects considered for KPDI funding shall meet the requirements
2 under KRS 154. 21-017.
3 Section 5. Whereas rural areas of Kentucky have been impacted by high
4 unemployment, an emergency is declared to exist, and this Act takes effect upon its
5 passage and approval by the Governor or upon its otherwise becoming a law.
